`converse-project-crud.spec.ts` delete conversation takes a while and failed 3 times in this run (https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/11167/overview/04bd880c-7445-44f2-86ef-2ccd76808df6/replay?roarHideRunsWithDiffGroupsAndTags=1&ts=1718164267380.6072&att=1). The api request for delete completes in 1 sec but the list of conversation in the side bar is not updated after delete completes. Maybe we need to wait for the next get all conversation request first before asserting?
cc @Aayush :ty:
